{"tid":1727561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[澳洲文宣]澳洲手足入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-16T13:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T08:57:14.000Z","uid":127783,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e81b62bf533a641f587ee58d881e158b4a925903","tid":1727561,"uid":127783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:12:57.000Z","msg":"Drew Pavlou 係UQ嘅senator 一直以黎幫左香港好多 組織左好多次rally 仲用UQ senator嘅身份喺UQ發左文章代表UQ譴責警暴 被UQ嘅支那教授喺大陸點名批評 受到大陸狗嘅死亡恐嚇 但UQ冇支援學生不特只仲要威脅佢將文章下架否則有penalty <br />\n<br />\nUQ奶共就不嬲嘅 但喺澳洲咁明顯地打壓言論自由都冇人理？希望澳洲手足幫手retweet. 希望多啲人關注呢件事 <br />\n<br />\n其實係澳洲核彈黎 集中推澳洲大學冇言論自由 被中國入侵 <br />\n<br />\n佢告左個支那教授 星期六上court<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/oct/23/queensland-student-sues-chinese-consul-general-alleging-he-incited-death-threats\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2019%2Foct%2F23%2Fqueensland-student-sues-chinese-consul-general-alleging-he-incited-death-threats&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=95ccd309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/oct/23/queensland-student-sues-chinese-consul-general-alleging-he-incited-death-threats</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/drewpavlou/status/1195143725673938945?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdrewpavlou%2Fstatus%2F1195143725673938945%3Fs%3D21&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=7a4dd5e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdrewpavlou%2Fstatus%2F1195143725673938945%3Fs%3D21&h=74b50c40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/drewpavlou/status/1195143725673938945?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://twitter.com/drewpavlou/status/1195143725673938945?s=21\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdrewpavlou%2Fstatus%2F1195143725673938945%3Fs%3D21&h=8cf6d219&s={SIZE}\" /><br /